description: This inviting 1-bedroom condo offers the rare convenience of deeded off-street parking! Step inside to an open-concept living room and kitchen, featuring elegant crown molding and gleaming hardwood floors throughout. The modern kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances—perfect for cooking and entertaining. The spacious bedroom includes a versatile bonus room, ideal for a home office, nursery, or walk-in closet, highlighted by an exposed brick wall for added character. Additional amenities include a tiled bathroom, a large private storage area, and convenient laundry facilities in the basement. Ideally located, you’re just moments from shops, restaurants, the “T”, #9 bus, Seaport, hospitals, and much more. Don’t miss this fantastic opportunity to own in one of South Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods!
